{"tid":1407120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"八五週一！罷工消費攻略！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T14:50:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T16:25:10.000Z","uid":277873,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"32eecf65741dc4c567fb598664a93520260e6ac5","tid":1407120,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:50:11.000Z","msg":"就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">一蚊都唔好用</span></span>！<br />\n你哋到底預備好<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">早午晚三餐</span></span></strong>未？你哋唔係諗住當平時集會遊行咁，順便出街食呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁辛苦罷工，之後去幫趁啲唔擋罷工既舖頭你無嘢呀？<br />\n外出集會<strong>記得自備飲料</strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有家常小菜當然好，頹到極，煮個麵加腸仔蛋，再頹啲杯麵都好。聽日罷得工就記得唔好出街買嘢食喇。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: maroon;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民罷工！<br />\nHongkongers Assemble !! </span></span>"},{"pid":"523e4b4e75fac36c90bae270d2e22549e8febfcd","tid":1407120,"uid":268237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T14:51:37.000Z","msg":"[集中討論]0730鑽石山地鐵<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1407061\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1407061</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"af7b49e432275d59a4a58fae74d6228246174172","tid":1407120,"uid":39568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n8月5日全港被罷工<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1405650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1405650</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"43c65039ff2e664548797d75a65992c086e65850","tid":1407120,"uid":277873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:06:52.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"5454842c4e943566f30d6e03bb024966b9622739","tid":1407120,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T15:29:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkg